Python
======

#### virtualenv [virtualenv github]
	1. create virtualenv ENV: `$ source ~/ENV/bin/activate`
	2. exit the env: $ deactivate
	3. install Anaconda: [Anaconda], specify the location: /Users/Damon/ENV/anaconda2
	   and cloud for Anaconda: https://anaconda.org

#### iPython
	1. upgrade with Jupyter
	2. installation: http://jupyter.readthedocs.io/en/latest/install.html
	3. `$ jupyter notebook`
	4. `$ pip install ipyparallel` and `$ ipcluster nbextension enable` to enable it


[virtualenv github]: (https://virtualenv.pypa.io/en/latest/userguide)
[Anaconda]: (https://www.continuum.io/downloads#_macosx)

#### Functional Language

1. language features that aid functional programing:
   * immutable data
   * first class functions
   * tail call optimisation

2. programming techniques used to write functional code:
   * mapping 
   * reducing 
   * pipelineing
   * recursing
   * currying 

3. advantageous properties of functional programs
   * parallelization
   * lazy evaluation
   * determinism

